Class SharePointSiteConfig

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.object.SharePointSiteConfig
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class SharePointSiteConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Configuration object that is used to drive unstructured collection from SharePoint site collections.

A SharePoint target collector config contains a list of these objects. It encapsulates the information necessary to traverse through a tree of sites in a sharepoint environment.
